==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Convertend
<hw>Con`ver*tend"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>convertenus</ets> to be converted.]</ety> <fld>(Logic)</fld>
<def>Any proposition which is subject to the process of conversion; --
so called in its relation to itself as converted, after which process it
is termed the <xex>converse</xex>. See <er>Converse</er>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Logic)</fld>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Converter</ent>⟦br⟧
